        {
          "date": "2026-07-10",
          "event": "currency_correction",
          "by": "peter.brackett@institutionaladviser.co.uk",
          "detail": "S&P confirmed directly that Money Manager Database exports default to USD platform-wide. The bottom-up alternate figure was mislabeled GBP throughout — it is actually $689.63bn USD, not £689.63bn. Corrected in-place (currency field added, note updated); GBP-equivalent at the 2026-07-10 spot rate (1.34 USD/GBP) is approximately £514.65bn. Active source (LGPS override, genuinely GBP) unchanged — this correction does not switch which number is shown on the site, but does change the size of the gap between the two."
